# Note: you can have up to about ~50 destinations. the script will take care of its memory and not accept more when memory runs out.
# Note: there is a possibility to rewrite this and store way more slurls but i thought 50 should be plenty? if not, contact Night Starchild
# Note: the format is: name=slurl <lookat> 

